snippet.title: Mineko's Night Market - Summer 2018 Trailer
snippet.description:
Mineko’s Night Market is a narrative-driven take on adventure/life simulation games about friendship, Japanese tradition, and many, many cats!
Coming to Nintendo Switch, PC & Mac in 2019.

You can WISHLIST it on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/762940/Minekos_Night_Market/

Follow us for updates: http://twitter.com/MinekosMarket

Download PressKit assets here: 
https://www.dropbox.com/sh/kddsr3519m9n8yu/AAAxY9UagR4cxyM3akQtKx0Xa?dl=0

Mineko's Night Market is being lovingly created by:
http://twitter.com/meowza
http://twitter.com/kukubee
